    "body": "I don't think we should make this change. This is only more intuitive in the same way that \"0/0 = 0\" could be seen as intuitive in math, but it is not a good axiom and 0/0 is undefined.\r\n\r\nThe initial minting of tokens should be delegated to another account or contract. But if you want to customize `_voteSucceeded` in your own Governor instance to add this behavior that's fine.",
